    <h3>How do I start tracking my headaches?</h3>
    <p>After creating an account, click on "New Headache Log" to record a new episode. Fill in details such as start time, intensity, duration, and any potential triggers or medications used.</p>
    <h3>Can I view my headache history?</h3>
    <p>Yes, the "Headache Logs" page displays all your recorded headaches. You can filter and sort these entries to identify patterns or trends.</p>
    <h3>How can I share my data with my doctor?</h3>
    <p>Use the "Generate Share Link" feature to create a secure, temporary link to your headache logs. You can send this link to your healthcare provider or display it during your appointment.</p>
